Title: Vault of the Incarnates: Fury of the Storm-Eater
Description:
No! We locked the Incarnates away to save this world and now Raszageth seeks to free them!

She cannot succeed, $n. All life on Azeroth is in grave danger if you do not stop her!

I shall return to Nozdormu at the Seat of the Aspects to plan for whatever is to come. But do not worry, I will not leave you without aid. Kalecgos and Khadgar will be sent to join you as you venture through the Vault.

Good luck, champion.
ObjectivesText: Enter the Vault of the Incarnates and defeat Raszageth.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak with Kalecgos at the Seat of the Aspects in Valdrakken.
